========================================================================
                      NOVA SENTINEL AGENT EXECUTABLE
========================================================================
Thank you for downloading the NovaSentinel Agent!

This is a mock executable file generated for development, demonstration,
and evaluation purposes.

In a production environment, this binary is compiled as a native C#
single-file self-contained background executable for Windows (x64),
running as a scheduled system service to collect local telemetry (CPU,
memory, storage, thermals, battery) and stream it periodically to the
SaaS console.

Agent capabilities:
-------------------
1. Low-overhead background system telemetry gathering.
2. Direct connection to the report ingestion API.
3. Automated scheduled reports every 7 days.
4. Intelligent local anomaly detection.

